{"tid":2499654,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[估名] 有人事顧問稱今年僱主聘用畢業生壓價或逾10%","createTime":"2021-04-22T05:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T05:47:50.000Z","uid":127905,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"88f2b5d4689696ba3db47e7422ca26340e4fc6ee","tid":2499654,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"毅知顧問公司董事總經理周綺萍表示，隨著疫苗接種、疫情緩和，今年就業情緒較去年樂觀，但失業率高企，毋需經驗的一般工種平均每1000名求職者爭一個職位，畢業生月薪亦較前年最少跌逾5%，目前約11000至14000元。<br />\n<br />\n她指，由於部分去年畢業的學生仍未找到工作，勞動人口供應過多，預期今年僱主聘用畢業生時會壓價，幅度有可能逾10%。<br />\n<br />\n周綺萍說，不鼓勵畢業生攻讀碩士後投身一般工種，因為企業或會認為應徵者學歷過份優秀，與職位設計不相稱，建議找不到長工的畢業生，考慮應徵合約工賺取經驗，同時要做好期望管理，明白僱主在市道差時會希望僱員能夠快速適應崗位、獨立投入工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586849-20210421.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586849-20210421.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=769da24b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586849-20210421.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5afb91ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586849-20210421.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ffa58121597ed09247625650fc90d3f62b586909","tid":2499654,"uid":41288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf3F4eDsrerkp1Xdj6b7sbST1wZRq45pTM8H5MTFkNoB6?filename=FtijHdt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtijHdt.gif&h=5c220f76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61bec63fa303755ec0c9a3f4f1978132c687623a","tid":2499654,"uid":155136,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"周綺萍 年年開新公司？公司名次次睇都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3479ce0073ad4529670b404fd2083f919ea03312","tid":2499654,"uid":225694